data.description: $50,000 price reduction! This beautiful home is so unique!  Entry is into a foyer,  welcoming guests into a  living area which has been opened to create a sexy great room with handsome built-ins throughout the home, constructed by renowned craftsman, Paul Kaufmann. The primary suite includes a large bathroom with a walk-in/roll-in shower, inviting soaking tub, walk in closet, and  conveniently located washer and dryer.  The second bedroom is being used as an office, but could have the closet restored.  There is a bonus room off the garage, with egress to the back yard. This is what I am indicating as a 3rd small bedroom. It could accommodate a closet or could be used as a studio, an office or a work-out room. There's even room to punch out and add a bathroom!  Pella doors and windows, copper plumbing, solid interior doors. The A/C unit was manufactured in 2019, and the roof is a lifetime metal roof. The quarter acre lot  has plenty of room for a pool, if desired. Close to shopping and dining.
